<span id="freeTextContainer17647563938038466811">Another good book, but another pretty tough time to read about. This book deals with the aftermath of the martyrdom of Joseph and Hyrum and the preparations to trek west to the Rocky Mountains. With the church departing Nauvoo, the Steed family has to come to the realization that with the different choices each person is making, their family is about to be split up and separated more than ever before.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


